    Dear Visitor!
</h2>
            <p class="text-center font-sans font-light text-black-m-300">Due to the high interest, and to make your purchase easier, a queueing system is in place on the website. You will soon be able to purchase your tickets!</p>
            <div>
                <!--[if BLOCK]><![endif]--><!--[if ENDBLOCK]><![endif]-->            </div>
            <p class="text-center font-sans font-light text-black-m-300">The number is continually and automatically updated. Please only refresh the page, if the number has not changed in the last 3 minutes.</p>

            <p class="mt-8">
                <a
                    class="font-sans font-light text-black-m-300 underline"
                    href="#"
